EXTENDED SIMPLE INTEGER LANGUAGE
--------------------------------

ESIL is a two-pass compiler for SIM(Simple Integer Machine) machine.

This was done as part of my labortary course work during the academic year 2011-12.

ESIL language description and SIM target machine description can be found in the READ-ME directory.

The generated Target Machine Code can be simulated using the simulator provided.

DEPENDENCIES
-------------
   (i)  gcc version 4


